Description:
    This will generate views, models and controller actions for forum.

Example:
    rails generate forum

    This will create:
      # views
      views/forum/forums
      views/forum/topics
      views/forum/comments

      # controllers
      controller/forum/forums_controller.rb
      controller/forum/topics_controller.rb
      controller/forum/comments_controller.rb

      # models
      model/forum.rb
      model/topic.rb
      model/comment.rb
